										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/nathanielmoore/">Nathaniel Moore</a></h6>
										Nathaniel Moore is a Southern writer whose work has appeared in <em>Politico</em>, <em>Slate</em>, <em>The New Republic</em>, <em>Liberties</em>, <em>Raritan</em>, and elsewhere.																			</div>
